    "We then use LLava Instruct data to improve the instruction understanding of our multimodal LLMs, creating our instruction tuning dataset FinVis-IT.",
    "While the FinVis-PT dataset includes stock market charts and asks simple questions about them, FinVis-IT is multi-turn and includes more complex charts and instructions.",
    "Our visual instruction datasets are described in Table 3.",
